Consumía demasiada memoria, era sólo C++, etc. <!-- 123 ¿?¿? -->ad naus.
Con la reciente versión del GNOME ORBit, podemos empezar a
desplegar CORBA en el GNOME.
<!-- 123 ***The big reason is that MICO was just unworkable. it took
too much memory, it was C++ only, etc. ad naus. With the
